Class MedicalOffice

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • spring.model.MedicalOffice

  • public class MedicalOffice
extends java.util.Observable
    Medical office class that serves as the central unit for the healthcare portal and keeps track of the healthcare providers, admin and patients for the medical office
